When you run a batch script or power shell script to execute maven command, it is similar to a script from outside and that script will run in its own way. It means your script is delegating a task to another script. There are two possibilities, the other may succeed or it may fail. You have track manually whether there is a failure. You have to in the following manner.

    set mvnBuildError=0
    if not errorlevel 0 set mvnBuildError=1
    if %mvnBuildError%==1 (
        REM do other stuffs
    )

